{"tid":1518989,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線同勇武入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-30T12:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:25:20.000Z","uid":69696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7a85f75573b5e1fb02098f84db071135147d50","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:07:22.000Z","msg":"翻譯左少少關於示威既有用資訊，希望你地睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>1. 裝備篇</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ATJamem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FATJamem.png&h=abbfb4d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">所有防具及武器要噴黑</span>。著一樣服裝既人群有展示力量及團結既效果，可以令對方畏懼。 <br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">大圍巾係比口罩好</span>，尤其係<span style=\"color: red;\">浸左醋、蘋果醋或檸檬汁</span>，可以<span style=\"color: red;\">減低TG及pepper spray既效果</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/DRXB1e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRXB1e9.jpg&h=7f7d0c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&bull; 上身防具可以用<span style=\"color: red;\">運動防具</span>，如越野電單車車手護甲，<span style=\"color: red;\">或捲起及痴實既發泡膠</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/HjoBgOK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjoBgOK.jpg&h=25e3140d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/to7RP8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fto7RP8L.jpg&h=3946a4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">前臂防具可用細o的既腳部護甲</span>代替，除左發泡膠之外可用<span style=\"color: red;\">捲起既雜誌</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/3EdJGff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EdJGff.jpg&h=dc970781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/UACZeAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUACZeAr.jpg&h=ffa75c62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>2. 武器篇 </ins></span><br />\n&bull;<span style=\"color: red;\"> 顏料彈</span>可以由兩種方法整：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/SNRWgPj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNRWgPj.png&h=11b18afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\na. 將顏料放係<span style=\"color: red;\">Condom</span>入面，索緊另一端。記得用投擲既方式掟，確保有足夠力道整爆佢。 <br />\nb. 係<span style=\"color: red;\">雞蛋頂部吉一個細loan</span>，上下大力chok之後倒晒強汁出黎。<span style=\"color: red;\">蛋乾之後用漏斗倒顏料入去</span>，再用膠紙封口。 <br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">起好路障之後要不停投擲物品，掟空玻璃樽</span>，落地爆開既時候可以嚇對方。 <br />\n&bull; 雞尾酒<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/8Htamf6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Htamf6.png&h=0de2d1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">擲物首要目標係指揮官、槍手、捉人隊伍如速龍隊</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地唔會有盾</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/br9kJuD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbr9kJuD.png&h=5f2255d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n譯自：<br />\nWarrior crowd control and riot manual <br />\n<a href=\"https://ia800303.us.archive.org/17/items/WarriorCrowdControlRiotManual/warrior_crowd_control.pdf?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=ios_app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fia800303.us.archive.org%2F17%2Fitems%2FWarriorCrowdControlRiotManual%2Fwarrior_crowd_control.pdf%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dios_app&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUikV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=527b5317\" target=\"_blank\">https://ia800303.us.archive.org/17/items/WarriorCrowdControlRiotManual/warrior_crowd_control.pdf?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=ios_app</a>"},{"pid":"69fcd3d39c1333826bfde93991b52fcfd7b47244","tid":1518989,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:07:54.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUikV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=bb5adcb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUikV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=d25a8915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUikV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=255a64d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUikV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=74813345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"a3640dd6475ac1d557295b90a41b5f5c42717109","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f99f4b4b9b06643e787a1cbfcb55c3ee8f15446","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca7625005c166ca2213e74c05e3729ab79e732d","tid":1518989,"uid":287064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"[P牌仔求推]除左要大嗌自己名，仲要講埋呢句！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1516180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1516180</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋呢個，對保護自己好有幫助"},{"pid":"066ab47a01e8259b7a4c368e77b8524d54e1fbba","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bad04656bdc4801660c498e43bb53f551f098a9","tid":1518989,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"883fe249a84963302f82590d3b892e23c9496544","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:37:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>3. 陣法及衝擊</ins></span><br />\n &bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">橫線陣</span>係警察常用陣法，<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點係側翼</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvrVUsF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvrVUsF.png&h=18a8190d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&bull;向前推進應該<span style=\"color: red;\">嗌一二一二，一係左腳，二係右</span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有盾，左腳遞出既就敲盾</span>，帶起士氣。<br />\n &bull; 捉人隊伍，亦即係速龍隊，由4－6人組成，通常企係橫線陣後面隱藏及被保護。捉人既時候橫線陣會打開缺口，兩人一組唔帶武器或盾牌去捉人，隊友就會係旁邊掩護。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xDpNNT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xDpNNT.png&h=8cc7319d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>4. 路障 </ins></span><br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">係最窄既地方起</span>。 <br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">如起係高地</span>，要<span style=\"color: red;\">從上而下</span>望向敵人。 <br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">橫放車軚</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">車軚中空既地方放滿浸滿汽油既膠袋或毛巾</span>。用火把點燃，製造出濃濃黑煙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjBiSeH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjBiSeH.png&h=42cce293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&bull; <span style=\"color: red;\">撤退時燒路障</span>，保護撤退既人同抵擋敵方。記得<span style=\"color: red;\">燒前將燃料如木、紙或汽油放滿路障</span>。  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>5. 應對衝擊 </ins></span><br />\n&bull; 用大量擲物或路障去拖慢或擊潰衝擊。<span style=\"color: red;\">撤退時快步或小跑，切忌好似癲佬咁跑</span>。保持鎮定及自信，<span style=\"color: red;\">同時間叫其他人冷靜</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">有裝備既人企最後保護後退既人</span>。"},{"pid":"b53db7e86aa35ec57b534a4a81508f1c8e9c116f","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc068e7a68a1bb3456c210c39ce4c82c3ccf41fc","tid":1518989,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日三點 中環遮打</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fcb3282ff7bae655048ecf9899c0994a1996cde1","tid":1518989,"uid":167903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:43:00.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"1a5d1ac77e1ea0199d428bdcb33e4c50bd309e34","tid":1518989,"uid":252510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ade9d8ab5494144a096541ae90d16a5ccf92af2","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:54:41.000Z","msg":"譯晒，係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa439714345418116e773e359e4b568ab077077","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea80c136baa9e618a0679d7900030e1b625eda6d","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144ac736a24d0edce65153f0ab0618e6d748529d","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cf4619707d2e6dc06c4c7d195a188f52078092","tid":1518989,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}